parameters.name: ExternalIp
parameters.description: The EIP in the DNAT entry. The public IP address is used to access the Internet.

parameters.name: ForwardEntryId
parameters.description: The ID of the DNAT entry.

parameters.name: ForwardEntryName
parameters.description: The name of the DNAT entry.

parameters.name: InternalIp
parameters.description: The private IP address of the instance that uses the DNAT entry for Internet communication.

parameters.name: IpProtocol
parameters.description:
The protocol. Valid values:

*   **TCP**: forwards TCP packets.
*   **UDP**: forwards UDP packets.
*   **Any**: forwards all packets.

parameters.name: NatGatewayId
parameters.description: The ID of the NAT gateway.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description:
The page number. Pages start from page **1**.

Default value: **1**.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries per page. Maximum value: **100**.

Default value: **10**.
